Customer: Ha bolo.

Abhi actually maine call kiya tha aapka jaise registered number hai na video meeting ka aapka jaise aaya tha India Mart par aur video meeting abhi jaise aapki ho gayi hai yahan se. To abhi matlab services mein aur koi problem to nahi hai na jaise unhone aapko explain kar diya hai sara video meeting par service ke regarding.

Executive: Hello. To main wahi puch rahi thi jaise abhi aapki video meeting yahan se ho chuki hai done to main abhi aapka na ticket open hua tha. To ticket main abhi yahan se close kar do na sir aapka.
Customer: Wo number pe phone kar lijiye na 98250.
Executive: Ek minute ek minute kya number hai. Ek minute aap mere ko number bata dijiye dobara. Line pe rahiyega.
Customer: 98250
Executive: Hmm. Aage?
